{"tid":2066493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲警案播片 警未認出施襲者","createTime":"2020-06-16T10:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T10:55:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"19c8cfb42b285e1e84713e2eeccd841cdb5408fa","tid":2066493,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200616/45RMFWLSCOGPRWR7ORFHQ4ZHOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2F45RMFWLSCOGPRWR7ORFHQ4ZHOQ%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=9b0e347f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2F45RMFWLSCOGPRWR7ORFHQ4ZHOQ%2F&h=6e17e5f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200616/45RMFWLSCOGPRWR7ORFHQ4ZHOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n襲警案播片 警未認出施襲者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KFGQGFJQWOJW3ZPN4AFU5CNMHI.jpgA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKFGQGFJQWOJW3ZPN4AFU5CNMHI.jpgA&h=dec1134f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年12月沙田新城市廣場發生警民衝突，一名大專男生被指高舉相機上前並踢警長，因而被控襲警。案件昨開審，聲稱遇襲的警長指當日現場環境十分混亂，坦言無法識別施襲者身份；另一警員供稱目睹涉案男生用腳施襲，但承認在案發影片中看不見男生。辯方指，當日男生一頭銀灰色短髮，易被識別，但案發片段中並沒有類似外形的施襲者。<br />\n<br />\n知專學生洪嘉榮（20歲，圖）被指去年12月15日在沙田港鐵站襲擊警長陳勁濤。陳事後經診斷為輕微腦震盪。<br />\n<br />\n陳供稱，當日現場有逾百人聚集叫囂，部份人向警方掟雜物。他制服一名男子時倒地，隨即被數人拳打腳踢。他同意現場環境十分惡劣、混亂及不安全，因周遭有人叫囂。。。。。。。。。。。。。。人士或會衝上前拍攝，吳當時集中注意力營救陳，並沒留意周遭人士的行為，吳表示「可以咁講」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官李志豪裁定表證成立。辯方結案陳詞指，陳確認影片拍下完。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，促裁定被告罪名不成立。案件下周二裁決。<br />\n案件編號：STCC4500/19<br />\n■記者劉偉琪"},{"pid":"a8ab03d9abd49943cd9e9fa77d9c11a21d2f3a57","tid":2066493,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"紅官: 警未認出施襲者 誠實可靠"},{"pid":"6a5191338b47c3b9a250a20cf6a554ada92792f7","tid":2066493,"uid":134744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"咁都表證成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncls"},{"pid":"88bc9e4d695492d0592ded661df681ec890ec81e","tid":2066493,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:26:09.000Z","msg":"準備投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f700a417f530f8fef514daa2d5edb4ab6105667","tid":2066493,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"認唔到又成立？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55c77059a22cb9fec0feb3ec65c68a9ad59ccb2","tid":2066493,"uid":310446,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a8ab03d9abd49943cd9e9fa77d9c11a21d2f3a57","tid":2066493,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"紅官: 警未認出施襲者 誠實可靠"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"紅官: 警未認出施襲者 代表暴徒偽裝度極高 <br />\n導致判決有困難<br />\n本席決定告多條妨礙司法公正 罪名正立"},{"pid":"0a870e951130d72b2ad47491284f13ec55542bff","tid":2066493,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"原來法官咁易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d30be5f877293170f7d37747f2570d3c004529d","tid":2066493,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a55c77059a22cb9fec0feb3ec65c68a9ad59ccb2","tid":2066493,"uid":310446,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a8ab03d9abd49943cd9e9fa77d9c11a21d2f3a57","tid":2066493,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"